# Config for nektos/act (https://github.com/nektos/act) — local GitHub Actions.
# act auto-sets ACT=true, which the workflows use to switch scripts into mock
# mode (FASTMAIL_MOCK_DIR=./mocks), so no real Fastmail token is ever needed.
-P ubuntu-latest=catthehacker/ubuntu:act-latest
--secret-file act/secrets.example
